summary: The mighty Sufferthorn from Oblivion returns!
descriptionHtml:
Sufferthorn, the Elven Dagger you received in Oblivion as a reward for one of the Dark Brotherhood contracts has been unearthed! Can you find the mighty dagger in any of the Sanctuaries of Skyrim? 

Location at Dawnstar Sanctuary! By the Night Mother (Needs testing of both during first visit and after its restored if anyone could do this please)
author: Hannah92
